				\begin{document}$$\sqrt{19}\times \sqrt{19}$$\end{document}), which was beyond the computational capability at the time that such theoretical works were conducted20–22. Although this study calculated the electronic surface energies (γelec) of more reconstructions compared to the previous works, including (111)B (19×19\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
